title: Aggregation of FCC, Online, AM Radio stations that carry Rush Limbaugh, USA, 2008 into USA Counties by State with FIPS Codes
name: Aggregation of FCC, Online, AM Radio stations that carry Rush Limbaugh, USA, 2008 into USA Counties by State with FIPS Codes
description: The point shape file shows locations of  523 AM radio stations that carry Rush Limbaugh, i.e., almost 10% of all AM radio stations in the USA. The shape file was generated by combining data scraped from online source (see URL cited) and the geocoded list of 5,097 AM radio stations in the USA (see the URL below).
